ChangeWatchers is an ActionForm
    action is ChangeUser
    title is "ChangeAdhocWatchersOnOrganizationsAndNotices"
    Layout
        single column
            RecallGroup
                display as text
        paragraph
            RecallAdhocUser
                label is "FromUser"
                display as text
            DerivedName
                no label
                display as text
        single column
            visible when (ChangeAll)
                InactivateCurrentUser
        paragraph
            ToUser
            ToUser.DerivedName
                no label
                display as text
        single column
            ChangeAll
            visible when (not ChangeAll)
                ChangeOpenNotices
                ChangeWatchers
